    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.87 * v1 + 0.44)) * (0.61 * v0))
    v2 = (wp.abs(0.94) - (v1 / (v2 + 0.56 * v0 + 0.89)))
    v0 = (0.15 - v1)
    v0 = 0.14
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs(v1))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.32)))
    tmp = 0.23
    v0 = v2
